features: HYPOALLERGENIC - Our super-soft baby wipes are approved by dermatologists and suitable for eczema-prone skin and allergy sufferers. They’re free from nasties like parabens and synthetic fragrances and are gentle on delicate skin, making them perfect newborn essentials

MADE FROM 99% WATER - We infuse our baby wet wipes with the gentlest organic chamomile, to soothe and soften sore skin. Made without the harsh chemicals, they’ll give your little one a gentle clean whilst protecting sensitive skin

BIODEGRADABLE - Kit & Kin’s eco wet wipes are biodegradable, made with sustainable plant-based materials and packed in recyclable packaging made from 50% recycled materials. So they’ll be better for your baby, and more conscious of our planet

EASY TO DISPENSE - We’ve made our sensitive baby wipes softer, stronger and easier to get out of the packet with just one hand. So, they’ll be easier for you to use, and even more gentle on your newborn’s delicate skin

PROTECTING YOUR WORLD NATURALLY - Every time you buy our baby essentials, you’re helping to protect our precious rainforests for future generations - as well as helping to provide education and healthcare to children in remote communities through the Kit & Kin Foundation
description: Product Description Meet our best baby wipes yet! Our new and improved formula means our hypoallergenic and biodegradable baby wipes are softer, stronger and even easier to dispense for quick nappy changes and easy clean-ups. Made with 99% water and dermatologist approved, they’ll be gentle on sensitive skin. Plus, every pack you buy protects our precious rainforests. Our wipes are made without: petrochemicals, alcohol, chlorine, parabens, SLS, formaldehyde carriers, phenols, lanolin or most common allergens. Patented easy dispense lid for quick nappy changes Recyclable packaging, made from 50% recycled materials Infused with soothing chamomile to calm and protect skin KINDER TO YOU Designed to be kind to the most sensitive skin, our hypoallergenic wipes are made with 99% water and are dermatologist approved. They're soft, strong, extra-large and easy to dispense, perfect for one-handed changes and wiping up spills. PLANET-CONSCIOUS Biodegradable, plastic-free and made from sustainably sourced plant-based materials, our wipes are the planet-conscious choice for your family. Our packaging is made using 40% recycled materials and is recyclable. PROTECTING OUR FUTURE We care for people and the planet through the Kit & Kin foundation. Every purchase you make supports our mission to keep our rivers and oceans clean, and to protect our precious rainforest for generations to come.
